projects.title: Baby Cry Reason Prediction
projects.description: Baby Cry Prediction is a ML based project created for the predicting the reason why an infant is crying.It has three four Claification ['Hungry', 'Sleepy', 'Pain', 'Uncomfortable']This project is aimed for the infants between 0 yrs-2 yrs.This is the stage where the infants can't express why an infant is crying.The main aim is to assist Young and newly parents find out why their child is crying.
